1
00:01:25,100 --> 00:01:29,990
[Youthful Glory]

2
00:01:30,160 --> 00:01:32,880
[Episode 5]

3
00:01:40,640 --> 00:01:41,759
It's you again.

4
00:01:41,840 --> 00:01:43,300
What unfortunate timing.

5
00:01:44,910 --> 00:01:46,240
More than unfortunate,

6
00:01:46,590 --> 00:01:48,320
it's sworn enemies crossing paths.

7
00:01:48,320 --> 00:01:50,400
Yet you two keep meeting unexpectedly.

8
00:01:50,400 --> 00:01:51,759
There must be some

9
00:01:51,759 --> 00:01:53,120
inexplicable bond.

10
00:01:54,560 --> 00:01:57,280
As the proverb goes, "Stay near vermilion, turn red; stay near ink, turn black."

11
00:01:57,280 --> 00:01:59,479
Shouldn't you fear this association

12
00:01:59,479 --> 00:02:01,320
will drown you in scandal?

13
00:02:01,480 --> 00:02:02,960
He's no saint—

14
00:02:02,960 --> 00:02:04,280
he eavesdrops on private conversations

15
00:02:04,280 --> 00:02:05,800
and forever flicks

16
00:02:05,800 --> 00:02:07,000
that pretentious fan

17
00:02:07,120 --> 00:02:07,800
about like

18
00:02:07,800 --> 00:02:08,960
some strutting peacock.

19
00:02:08,960 --> 00:02:10,690
You're always waving that fan.

20
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:13,280
How could I possibly eavesdrop?

21
00:02:13,280 --> 00:02:14,560
You're practically shouting.

22
00:02:14,560 --> 00:02:15,560
It's impossible not to hear you!

23
00:02:15,560 --> 00:02:16,360
Honestly,

24
00:02:16,360 --> 00:02:17,960
you needn't worry about what kind of wife

25
00:02:17,960 --> 00:02:19,120
Second Young Master Shu will take.

26
00:02:19,120 --> 00:02:21,000
It certainly won't be

27
00:02:21,000 --> 00:02:21,720
a rude, unreasonable,

28
00:02:21,720 --> 00:02:23,520
domineering shrew like you!

29
00:02:24,350 --> 00:02:26,000
Who I am is beyond

30
00:02:26,000 --> 00:02:27,120
the judgment of

31
00:02:27,120 --> 00:02:28,680
a petty, frivolous dandy like you!

32
00:02:28,680 --> 00:02:29,440
Besides,

33
00:02:29,800 --> 00:02:30,680
I'm not

34
00:02:30,680 --> 00:02:31,880
speaking for myself.

35
00:02:32,000 --> 00:02:33,560
I'm thinking of our Tan

36
00:02:33,840 --> 00:02:35,840
is gentle and refined, learned in classics and decorum,

37
00:02:35,840 --> 00:02:37,600
with peerless grace and talent.

38
00:02:37,600 --> 00:02:40,400
She and Second Young Master Shu would make a well-matched pair.

39
00:02:40,400 --> 00:02:41,660
You're exaggerating.

40
00:02:43,800 --> 00:02:46,329
Does Miss Ming fancy Second Young Master Shu?

41
00:02:48,360 --> 00:02:49,720
Whether I fancy him or not

42
00:02:49,720 --> 00:02:50,800
is none of your concern.

43
00:02:50,800 --> 00:02:52,360
All I wish is that we never

44
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:54,760
cross paths again—no ties, no encounters.

45
00:02:58,000 --> 00:02:59,000
They must be heading to

46
00:02:59,000 --> 00:03:00,600
tour the Xian River now.

47
00:03:00,600 --> 00:03:02,800
Aren't you going to take a look?

48
00:03:04,440 --> 00:03:05,700
None of your business.

49
00:03:06,280 --> 00:03:07,400
It's just an eyesore.

50
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,400
Better not to see, the less to vex the heart.

51
00:03:09,400 --> 00:03:09,960
Miss,

52
00:03:10,240 --> 00:03:11,840
you're turning a blind eye

53
00:03:11,840 --> 00:03:13,370
and only fooling yourself.

54
00:03:16,680 --> 00:03:17,560
Why waste words

55
00:03:17,560 --> 00:03:18,620
on the irrelevant?

56
00:03:18,680 --> 00:03:19,240
Let's go.

57
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:30,560
Greetings, Your Majesty.

58
00:03:31,440 --> 00:03:33,040
I won't beat around the bush.

59
00:03:33,400 --> 00:03:34,530
I summoned you today

60
00:03:34,600 --> 00:03:37,260
for the marriage decree we discussed last time.

61
00:03:37,960 --> 00:03:38,760
Your Majesty,

62
00:03:43,120 --> 00:03:44,840
I...

63
00:03:44,880 --> 00:03:47,560
Do you know that the Empress Dowager,

64
00:03:47,960 --> 00:03:49,680
displeased with your repeated refusals,

65
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:51,810
has already issued an imperial edict?

66
00:03:53,280 --> 00:03:54,120
Your Majesty,

67
00:03:54,160 --> 00:03:55,720
Empress Dowager is unwilling

68
00:03:55,720 --> 00:03:57,000
to bother with appearances.

69
00:03:57,000 --> 00:03:59,200
She's forcing this marriage outright.

70
00:03:59,680 --> 00:04:00,600
But I can give you

71
00:04:00,600 --> 00:04:01,530
another choice.

72
00:04:05,580 --> 00:04:06,840
Take a look at the match I've chosen for your daughter.

73
00:04:06,840 --> 00:04:08,590
What do you think of him?

74
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:11,480
Marquis of Jing'an, please have a look.

75
00:04:15,080 --> 00:04:16,740
Actually, a child's marriage

76
00:04:16,920 --> 00:04:19,040
is not something that lies within your authority.

77
00:04:19,040 --> 00:04:20,480
Don't worry too much.

78
00:04:20,959 --> 00:04:23,600
No need to overthink—just judge the person.

79
00:04:23,970 --> 00:04:25,480
Can what the Empress Dowager

80
00:04:25,480 --> 00:04:26,920
picked for you even compare with

81
00:04:26,820 --> 00:04:28,940
[The Ming family's fourth daughter, is refined, dignified, prudent, and wise.]

82
00:04:27,360 --> 00:04:28,600
what I have chosen?

83
00:04:28,960 --> 00:04:31,000
[She is now of marriageable age and is hereby specially granted in marriage
to Jiang Xu, the Prince of Dingbei, and officially titled the Princess of Dingbei.]

84
00:04:34,420 --> 00:04:35,180
Your Majesty,

85
00:04:35,180 --> 00:04:35,800
well...

86
00:04:35,800 --> 00:04:36,400
Well...

87
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:38,000
Well...

88
00:04:39,140 --> 00:04:39,720
Well...

89
00:04:40,720 --> 00:04:42,020
Please allow me

90
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,840
some more time to consider.

91
00:04:44,040 --> 00:04:46,040
The Empress Dowager's edict has been issued.

92
00:04:46,040 --> 00:04:47,240
I went to great lengths

93
00:04:47,240 --> 00:04:49,240
to have it temporarily suppressed.

94
00:04:49,240 --> 00:04:51,100
But what can be held back for a time

95
00:04:51,159 --> 00:04:52,710
cannot be held back forever.

96
00:04:52,710 --> 00:04:54,400
It may reach your manor

97
00:04:54,530 --> 00:04:56,480
before you leave the palace.

98
00:04:56,960 --> 00:04:59,360
An imperial edict from the Empress Dowager!

99
00:04:58,900 --> 00:05:04,980
[Spring Blossoms and Autumn Fruits]

100
00:05:06,720 --> 00:05:10,120
Ming Tan of Marquis of Jing'an's Mansion—receive the edict!

101
00:05:11,850 --> 00:05:13,170
Eunuch,

102
00:05:13,200 --> 00:05:15,600
Fourth Miss isn't home right now.

103
00:05:15,620 --> 00:05:17,420
Send someone to look for her now.

104
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:20,280
Empress Dowager values protocol the most!

105
00:05:20,360 --> 00:05:21,690
This edict announcement

106
00:05:21,690 --> 00:05:23,570
must not be taken lightly.

107
00:05:23,600 --> 00:05:24,280
Yes.

108
00:05:24,920 --> 00:05:25,680
Go now!

109
00:05:25,920 --> 00:05:26,560
Yes.

110
00:05:27,600 --> 00:05:28,730
Marquis of Jing'an,

111
00:05:29,140 --> 00:05:30,800
why are you hesitating?

112
00:05:31,230 --> 00:05:33,159
Had he not asked me himself,

113
00:05:33,159 --> 00:05:34,260
I wouldn't have...

114
00:05:34,360 --> 00:05:34,920
Marry...

115
00:05:38,100 --> 00:05:39,830
I will marry my daughter to him.

116
00:05:41,800 --> 00:05:42,460
Liu Yiding!

117
00:05:43,280 --> 00:05:44,040
Here!

118
00:05:44,360 --> 00:05:46,920
Deliver the edict to the Marquis of Jing'an's Mansion at once.

119
00:05:46,920 --> 00:05:47,600
Yes.

120
00:05:53,590 --> 00:05:54,360
Wait.

121
00:05:55,600 --> 00:05:58,800
Tan isn't home today.

122
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,600
Second Young Master Shu.

123
00:06:03,600 --> 00:06:04,480
Why did Second Young Master Shu

124
00:06:04,480 --> 00:06:05,800
dismount and turn back?

125
00:06:05,800 --> 00:06:07,330
Isn't everyone supposed to

126
00:06:07,800 --> 00:06:08,800
head to the Xian River

127
00:06:08,800 --> 00:06:09,920
after the parade?

128
00:06:12,620 --> 00:06:13,480
Second Young Master Shu

129
00:06:13,480 --> 00:06:15,010
seems to be coming this way.

130
00:06:18,680 --> 00:06:20,080
Second Young Master Shu.

131
00:06:24,310 --> 00:06:26,120
Miss Bai. Miss Ming.

132
00:06:28,630 --> 00:06:30,620
Second Young Master Shu has placed third in the exams—

133
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:31,840
well deserved.

134
00:06:32,360 --> 00:06:33,840
Congratulations!

135
00:06:34,230 --> 00:06:35,600
Thank you, Miss Ming.

136
00:06:37,350 --> 00:06:38,600
He talked to you.

137
00:06:38,600 --> 00:06:40,600
He said thank you for your blessing!

138
00:06:42,480 --> 00:06:43,240
I wondered who

139
00:06:43,240 --> 00:06:45,310
was clinging to Second Young Master Shu.

140
00:06:45,310 --> 00:06:46,480
It turns out it's Miss Ming,

141
00:06:46,480 --> 00:06:48,140
the one who just got rejected.

142
00:06:52,240 --> 00:06:54,600
You're still looking radiant;

143
00:06:55,360 --> 00:06:56,960
seems the broken engagement

144
00:06:57,000 --> 00:06:58,400
didn't affect you at all.

145
00:06:59,920 --> 00:07:01,480
Thank you for your compliment.

146
00:07:01,480 --> 00:07:03,360
Didn't you vow to pray at Hanyan Temple

147
00:07:03,360 --> 00:07:05,160
for 49 days?

148
00:07:06,480 --> 00:07:08,610
Why are you back in the capital so soon?

149
00:07:13,040 --> 00:07:14,320
Second Young Master Shu.

150
00:07:14,320 --> 00:07:16,710
[Yunzhou]

151
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:17,040
A rare guest!

152
00:07:17,160 --> 00:07:18,800
Greetings, Princess of Fengzhao.

153
00:07:18,800 --> 00:07:20,530
Young Master Zhang is here too?

154
00:07:20,610 --> 00:07:23,960
[Yunzhou]

155
00:07:20,720 --> 00:07:21,800
I'll wait for Second Young Master Shu here.

156
00:07:21,800 --> 00:07:23,240
He's seasick

157
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:25,100
and can't swim across Xian River.

158
00:07:25,560 --> 00:07:26,720
I knew early on that

159
00:07:26,800 --> 00:07:29,360
Second Young Master Shu was not an ordinary person.

160
00:07:29,360 --> 00:07:32,960
It's only a matter of time before he tops the exam and ranks third.

161
00:07:33,400 --> 00:07:35,130
Thank you for your compliment.

162
00:07:38,280 --> 00:07:40,360
Miss Ming is dressed so flamboyantly

163
00:07:40,360 --> 00:07:41,620
for the street outing.

164
00:07:41,909 --> 00:07:44,560
Could it be that you just broke off the engagement

165
00:07:44,560 --> 00:07:47,290
and are now eager to find a new match for yourself?

166
00:07:47,400 --> 00:07:49,720
Enough! I've been very patient with you...

167
00:07:49,720 --> 00:07:51,240
My elaborate makeup

168
00:07:51,409 --> 00:07:52,270
is simply because

169
00:07:52,270 --> 00:07:54,330
I don't want to be burdened by my past.

170
00:07:55,000 --> 00:07:56,480
As for marriage,

171
00:07:56,720 --> 00:07:58,400
it has always been a matter decided by parents.

172
00:07:58,400 --> 00:08:00,040
I have no say in it.

173
00:08:00,600 --> 00:08:02,200
Looking at the whole of Xian,

174
00:08:02,240 --> 00:08:03,360
there are few daughters

175
00:08:03,360 --> 00:08:05,160
as fortunate as you—

176
00:08:05,360 --> 00:08:07,160
who are favored by the Empress Dowager's grace and care,

177
00:08:07,160 --> 00:08:09,600
and able to marry Prince of Dingbei,

178
00:08:09,800 --> 00:08:12,160
such a rare and outstanding husband.

179
00:08:13,000 --> 00:08:15,160
I've heard that his mansion has no other woman.

180
00:08:15,160 --> 00:08:16,360
Once you marry in,

181
00:08:16,360 --> 00:08:17,800
you'll be the sole favored lady of the household.

182
00:08:17,800 --> 00:08:19,480
Even the mansion's garden,

183
00:08:19,720 --> 00:08:22,240
famous in the capital for its unmatched peonies,

184
00:08:22,240 --> 00:08:24,120
is said to be for your eyes alone.

185
00:08:25,390 --> 00:08:26,560
Do you know

186
00:08:26,640 --> 00:08:28,480
why the peonies in the Prince of Dingbei's garden

187
00:08:28,480 --> 00:08:30,840
bloom so exceptionally beautifully?

188
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:34,960
I don't know.

189
00:08:35,840 --> 00:08:36,840
I heard that

190
00:08:37,880 --> 00:08:39,080
the Prince of Dingbei

191
00:08:39,240 --> 00:08:41,650
brutally killed all concubines of the mansion

192
00:08:41,650 --> 00:08:43,000
and buried them in the garden.

193
00:08:43,000 --> 00:08:44,560
Then, with their blood and flesh,

194
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:46,430
he nourished that line of peonies.

195
00:08:46,430 --> 00:08:47,480
My goodness.

196
00:08:53,000 --> 00:08:54,480
Really?

197
00:08:57,240 --> 00:08:58,520
Please forgive me.

198
00:08:59,010 --> 00:09:00,600
These are just some rumors

199
00:09:00,600 --> 00:09:01,320
our Minmin overheard

200
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,760
around town—

201
00:09:03,080 --> 00:09:04,960
idle gossip repeated without much thought.

202
00:09:04,960 --> 00:09:06,440
A fierce and bloodthirsty man

203
00:09:06,440 --> 00:09:08,000
like the Prince of Dingbei

204
00:09:08,000 --> 00:09:09,130
is far beyond the reach of

205
00:09:09,130 --> 00:09:11,360
ordinary folks like us.

206
00:09:11,990 --> 00:09:13,640
Only someone

207
00:09:13,670 --> 00:09:15,360
as noble and precious as you

208
00:09:15,360 --> 00:09:16,500
could be a worthy match for him.

209
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:17,640
When the time comes for your wedding,

210
00:09:17,640 --> 00:09:19,290
we will line the streets to send you off

211
00:09:19,290 --> 00:09:20,620
and celebrate with you.

212
00:09:22,130 --> 00:09:23,930
I just broke off the engagement.

213
00:09:24,070 --> 00:09:26,360
I won't share a room with you,

214
00:09:26,360 --> 00:09:27,720
lest my bad luck

215
00:09:27,720 --> 00:09:29,240
rub off on you

216
00:09:29,240 --> 00:09:30,640
and affect your

217
00:09:30,640 --> 00:09:31,720
blessed marriage.

218
00:09:36,840 --> 00:09:39,120
Here comes the imperial edict!

219
00:09:39,970 --> 00:09:44,270
[Clear Waters and Bright Woods]

220
00:09:40,180 --> 00:09:43,300
Ming Tan of the Ming family is to receive the decree!

221
00:09:58,970 --> 00:10:02,950
[Ode to Prosperity and Peace]

222
00:09:59,170 --> 00:10:02,480
The Ming family's fourth daughter, is refined, dignified,

223
00:10:02,480 --> 00:10:05,000
prudent, and wise

224
00:10:05,080 --> 00:10:07,600
and is now of marriageable age.

225
00:10:07,640 --> 00:10:09,260
She is hereby specially granted in marriage

226
00:10:09,260 --> 00:10:10,810
to Jiang Xu, the Prince of Dingbei,

227
00:10:10,810 --> 00:10:12,760
and officially titled the Princess of Dingbei.

228
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,480
Relevant officials are to select an auspicious date for the ceremony.

229
00:10:14,480 --> 00:10:15,720
Prepare the ceremonial gifts

230
00:10:15,720 --> 00:10:18,840
and formalize the decree. Carry it out as written.

231
00:10:21,130 --> 00:10:22,360
Who's being summoned?

232
00:10:22,360 --> 00:10:23,120
You...

233
00:10:25,320 --> 00:10:27,840
What am I being appointed as?

234
00:10:27,840 --> 00:10:29,040
Princess of Dingbei.

235
00:10:29,090 --> 00:10:31,380
That's what happens when you spit into the wind—

236
00:10:31,380 --> 00:10:33,480
it hits you right back.

237
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:43,480
Tan!

238
00:10:43,690 --> 00:10:44,240
Tan!

239
00:10:44,950 --> 00:10:45,600
Tan!

240
00:10:48,780 --> 00:10:51,820
[Spring Blossoms and Autumn Fruits]

241
00:10:52,840 --> 00:10:53,880
Slow down.

242
00:10:54,120 --> 00:10:55,780
So this marriage arrangement

243
00:10:55,810 --> 00:10:57,520
was agreed to by you?

244
00:10:57,600 --> 00:10:58,720
Of course.

245
00:10:59,760 --> 00:11:00,520
No, no.

246
00:11:00,520 --> 00:11:02,200
You don't know that

247
00:11:02,240 --> 00:11:03,240
today, the Empress Dowager

248
00:11:03,240 --> 00:11:04,980
also issued an imperial marriage decree.

249
00:11:04,980 --> 00:11:06,240
There is more than one.

250
00:11:06,520 --> 00:11:07,360
The first

251
00:11:07,360 --> 00:11:09,000
was intercepted by His Majesty,

252
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,120
but she can draft, persuade,

253
00:11:10,120 --> 00:11:11,120
and affix seals.

254
00:11:11,220 --> 00:11:12,200
When one decree failed,

255
00:11:12,200 --> 00:11:13,730
she simply issued another.

256
00:11:14,070 --> 00:11:15,730
Knowing His Majesty urgently

257
00:11:15,840 --> 00:11:17,360
summoned me today

258
00:11:17,360 --> 00:11:19,240
to discuss the marriage,

259
00:11:19,720 --> 00:11:20,840
the Empress Dowager didn't even notify us

260
00:11:20,840 --> 00:11:21,760
before delivering the second decree

261
00:11:21,760 --> 00:11:23,360
directly to our mansion.

262
00:11:23,380 --> 00:11:25,360
Then... What about the decree

263
00:11:25,360 --> 00:11:26,240
at the Wentao Pavilion?

264
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:28,720
That was my quick thinking!

265
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,440
I knew you wouldn't be

266
00:11:30,440 --> 00:11:31,640
at the mansion today,

267
00:11:31,840 --> 00:11:34,600
and the Empress Dowager strictly observes protocol.

268
00:11:34,600 --> 00:11:36,600
She'd never issue a decree

269
00:11:36,600 --> 00:11:38,600
with only a concubine present at the mansion.

270
00:11:38,600 --> 00:11:40,720
So I informed His Majesty

271
00:11:40,720 --> 00:11:42,880
of your whereabouts

272
00:11:42,880 --> 00:11:44,320
at the Wentao Pavilion.

273
00:11:45,200 --> 00:11:46,720
With the decree proclaimed

274
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:48,120
before a crowd,

275
00:11:48,360 --> 00:11:50,120
it became irreversible.

276
00:11:53,720 --> 00:11:55,600
Admittedly circuitous,

277
00:11:56,240 --> 00:11:58,370
but ultimately satisfactory for all.

278
00:11:58,840 --> 00:12:00,100
What's wrong with you?

279
00:12:00,840 --> 00:12:03,100
You must be tired from praying to Buddha.

280
00:12:04,360 --> 00:12:05,520
Have a good rest.

281
00:12:06,360 --> 00:12:07,960
I won't disturb you anymore.

282
00:12:15,060 --> 00:12:15,880
Oh no.

283
00:12:17,440 --> 00:12:18,480
I'm such a jinx.

284
00:12:18,480 --> 00:12:19,960
Everything I said is coming true.

285
00:12:19,960 --> 00:12:20,760
If the Prince of Dingbei

286
00:12:20,760 --> 00:12:21,960
is really anything like the rumors say,

287
00:12:21,960 --> 00:12:22,360
what are you

288
00:12:22,360 --> 00:12:23,480
going to do then?

289
00:12:23,480 --> 00:12:25,080
Father must think he's

290
00:12:25,170 --> 00:12:25,880
pulled off

291
00:12:25,900 --> 00:12:27,760
something brilliantly clever,

292
00:12:29,120 --> 00:12:30,240
but this marriage

293
00:12:30,480 --> 00:12:33,340
is even trickier than the one with the Liang family.

294
00:12:33,760 --> 00:12:35,600
Truly, I underestimated Uncle—

295
00:12:35,640 --> 00:12:37,840
that supposedly uncouth military man.

296
00:12:38,880 --> 00:12:41,480
But why does it have to be the Prince of Dingbei?

297
00:12:42,240 --> 00:12:42,760
Isn't he

298
00:12:42,760 --> 00:12:44,760
just another rough, violent brute?

299
00:12:45,320 --> 00:12:46,880
His bloodthirsty, cruel reputation

300
00:12:46,880 --> 00:12:48,740
is known throughout the capital.

301
00:12:49,000 --> 00:12:50,730
If he can be granted a marriage,

302
00:12:50,760 --> 00:12:51,720
then why not

303
00:12:51,720 --> 00:12:53,120
Second Young Master Shu?

304
00:12:53,720 --> 00:12:56,480
I prayed so sincerely before the Buddha

305
00:12:56,640 --> 00:12:57,960
for a top-ranking scholar

306
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,360
with outstanding looks.

307
00:13:00,600 --> 00:13:02,400
Did the Buddha not hear me right?

308
00:13:02,960 --> 00:13:03,600
Tan,

309
00:13:03,720 --> 00:13:04,980
don't be discouraged.

310
00:13:05,360 --> 00:13:06,440
We haven't seen

311
00:13:06,440 --> 00:13:07,640
him yet.

312
00:13:07,640 --> 00:13:08,720
When we see him,

313
00:13:08,720 --> 00:13:10,000
maybe he's not as bad

314
00:13:10,000 --> 00:13:11,120
as the rumors say?

315
00:13:11,440 --> 00:13:12,720
Did you not see

316
00:13:12,720 --> 00:13:14,000
how wild and arrogant he was

317
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:16,260
at the Lantern Festival Palace banquet?

318
00:13:16,840 --> 00:13:18,120
If I marry him,

319
00:13:19,360 --> 00:13:20,120
who knows

320
00:13:20,120 --> 00:13:21,980
when I might lose my head with him.

321
00:13:22,510 --> 00:13:23,600
Not necessarily.

322
00:13:23,720 --> 00:13:25,450
But the most important thing is

323
00:13:26,200 --> 00:13:27,880
he's a brute!

324
00:13:28,760 --> 00:13:32,480
He must also be ugly;

325
00:13:35,360 --> 00:13:37,900
then he truly has nothing going for him.

326
00:13:38,640 --> 00:13:39,340
No.

327
00:13:41,000 --> 00:13:42,860
This marriage must be cancelled.

328
00:13:43,010 --> 00:13:45,350
[Lilies of the River and Fragrant Angelicas of the Marsh]

329
00:13:47,640 --> 00:13:48,600
Father.

330
00:13:48,600 --> 00:13:49,480
Uncle.

331
00:13:51,760 --> 00:13:52,600
Well...

332
00:13:52,730 --> 00:13:53,970
What's going on here?

333
00:13:54,350 --> 00:13:54,880
Here.

334
00:13:54,880 --> 00:13:55,960
Alright, no need to help me.

335
00:13:55,960 --> 00:13:57,820
Uncle must be hungry. Have a seat.

336
00:14:00,080 --> 00:14:01,880
Have some bird's nest porridge.

337
00:14:03,480 --> 00:14:04,120
You...

338
00:14:05,890 --> 00:14:07,600
Tan has always been filial.

339
00:14:07,600 --> 00:14:08,720
What are you

340
00:14:09,720 --> 00:14:11,080
scheming now?

341
00:14:11,600 --> 00:14:14,330
It's all because of that sudden marriage decree.

342
00:14:15,720 --> 00:14:16,480
Father,

343
00:14:17,120 --> 00:14:19,050
the royal edict came too abruptly.

344
00:14:19,360 --> 00:14:20,360
I know nothing

345
00:14:20,360 --> 00:14:21,780
about the Prince of Dingbei.

346
00:14:21,780 --> 00:14:23,360
Of course I feel uneasy.

347
00:14:26,120 --> 00:14:27,200
I understand.

348
00:14:28,360 --> 00:14:29,480
After all,

349
00:14:29,480 --> 00:14:30,840
you'll be expected to be a proper match

350
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:32,300
for the Prince of Dingbei.

351
00:14:32,320 --> 00:14:34,200
It's a good thing

352
00:14:34,200 --> 00:14:36,200
to learn more about him beforehand.

353
00:14:37,000 --> 00:14:39,060
Who wants to be a proper match for him?

354
00:14:39,200 --> 00:14:41,060
I just want to know him well enough

355
00:14:41,120 --> 00:14:43,640
to figure out how to break off this engagement.

356
00:14:43,640 --> 00:14:46,000
Then, Father, do you know much about

357
00:14:46,120 --> 00:14:47,380
the Prince of Dingbei?

358
00:14:47,480 --> 00:14:49,760
Among the younger generation in Xian,

359
00:14:49,760 --> 00:14:51,880
few can truly command troops.

360
00:14:52,760 --> 00:14:54,170
But the Prince of Dingbei,

361
00:14:54,170 --> 00:14:55,600
at a very young age,

362
00:14:55,830 --> 00:14:57,640
led 3,000 elite soldiers

363
00:14:57,640 --> 00:15:00,000
to hold off 30,000 northern barbarians.

364
00:15:00,360 --> 00:15:02,000
That battle

365
00:15:02,600 --> 00:15:04,840
was said to be a sea of blood,

366
00:15:04,860 --> 00:15:06,860
with corpses stretching for miles.

367
00:15:07,200 --> 00:15:08,000
When enemy spies

368
00:15:08,000 --> 00:15:09,600
fall into his hands,

369
00:15:09,840 --> 00:15:11,840
a bit of blood and gore is nothing.

370
00:15:12,000 --> 00:15:13,600
They end up so mangled they're barely human,

371
00:15:13,600 --> 00:15:15,320
and when their bodies are thrown back,

372
00:15:15,320 --> 00:15:17,650
even their own army can't recognize them.

373
00:15:18,120 --> 00:15:19,320
It was because of this

374
00:15:19,640 --> 00:15:21,900
that things stayed quiet for half a year.

375
00:15:23,360 --> 00:15:25,290
And in the third year of Chengkang,

376
00:15:25,640 --> 00:15:26,840
the Prince of Dingbei

377
00:15:26,840 --> 00:15:28,880
hung the body of the barbarian chieftain's son

378
00:15:28,880 --> 00:15:30,240
on the city gate

379
00:15:30,240 --> 00:15:31,480
for three days.

380
00:15:32,080 --> 00:15:34,410
By the end, it had dried into a human jerky.

381
00:15:37,720 --> 00:15:40,080
So, the Prince of Dingbei

382
00:15:41,120 --> 00:15:43,360
is truly a remarkable talent.

383
00:15:44,360 --> 00:15:46,720
Having such a perfect son-in-law

384
00:15:47,120 --> 00:15:49,320
is truly a blessing for the Ming family.

385
00:15:51,320 --> 00:15:52,120
And

386
00:15:53,200 --> 00:15:54,480
though he is a general,

387
00:15:54,760 --> 00:15:56,320
he is tall

388
00:15:56,640 --> 00:15:57,840
and handsome,

389
00:15:58,000 --> 00:15:59,200
not at all inferior to the top scholar

390
00:15:59,200 --> 00:16:00,730
we saw parading yesterday.

391
00:16:02,960 --> 00:16:04,290
Uncle, are you serious?

392
00:16:06,000 --> 00:16:08,960
Well, compared to

393
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:10,240
when I was young,

394
00:16:16,320 --> 00:16:18,580
I suppose I had a bit more charm and grace.

395
00:16:19,600 --> 00:16:20,860
Are you clear about it?

396
00:16:22,240 --> 00:16:24,500
If you're clear about it, then let's eat.

397
00:16:28,310 --> 00:16:31,980
[Lilies of the River and Fragrant Angelicas of the Marsh]

398
00:16:30,120 --> 00:16:32,250
Tan, have you really made up your mind?

399
00:16:33,830 --> 00:16:35,000
Go see him once.

400
00:16:35,320 --> 00:16:36,980
If he really is as terrible as the rumors say,

401
00:16:36,980 --> 00:16:38,460
even the emperor's decree

402
00:16:38,490 --> 00:16:39,520
won't stop me

403
00:16:39,540 --> 00:16:41,340
from breaking off the marriage.

404
00:16:41,770 --> 00:16:43,650
You can't just listen to Uncle.

405
00:16:43,840 --> 00:16:45,840
Although he's a warrior,

406
00:16:45,840 --> 00:16:47,240
he probably wasn't so bad

407
00:16:47,480 --> 00:16:49,240
when he was young.

408
00:16:49,240 --> 00:16:50,200
Besides,

409
00:16:50,240 --> 00:16:52,170
didn't he say the Prince of Dingbei

410
00:16:53,830 --> 00:16:55,470
was a little better?

411
00:16:56,260 --> 00:16:58,680
Though he can't be called exceptionally handsome,

412
00:16:58,680 --> 00:17:00,400
he still has presence.

413
00:17:02,360 --> 00:17:03,920
Appearance matters,

414
00:17:04,339 --> 00:17:06,470
but character is even more important.

415
00:17:06,480 --> 00:17:07,560
They say the face reflects the heart,

416
00:17:07,560 --> 00:17:09,140
and one's words and actions reveal their true nature.

417
00:17:09,140 --> 00:17:10,819
From what I've seen of him,

418
00:17:10,849 --> 00:17:11,829
you can get a sense of

419
00:17:11,829 --> 00:17:12,829
his personality.

420
00:17:14,240 --> 00:17:16,440
But the Capital Garrison's defenses are tight,

421
00:17:16,440 --> 00:17:17,440
and the Prince of Dingbei is known for

422
00:17:17,440 --> 00:17:18,680
being rough and overbearing.

423
00:17:18,680 --> 00:17:19,880
I worry it might not be wise

424
00:17:19,880 --> 00:17:21,540
for you to rush in unprepared.

425
00:17:23,200 --> 00:17:25,200
Nothing ventured, nothing gained.

426
00:17:25,369 --> 00:17:26,960
As long as I can see him

427
00:17:27,040 --> 00:17:28,840
without revealing my identity,

428
00:17:29,570 --> 00:17:31,030
there won't be any danger.

429
00:17:31,920 --> 00:17:33,310
See him

430
00:17:33,560 --> 00:17:35,760
