432
00:18:00,320 --> 00:18:01,720
Stop! Who are you?

433
00:18:05,720 --> 00:18:07,280
We're from the Ming family,

434
00:18:06,770 --> 00:18:08,710
[Marquis of Jing'an's Mansion]

435
