437
00:18:10,350 --> 00:18:11,960
to Young General Shen.

438
00:18:13,740 --> 00:18:14,400
Come in.

439
00:18:18,010 --> 00:18:19,080
Come with me.

440
00:18:23,830 --> 00:18:24,240
Later,

441
00:18:24,240 --> 00:18:25,480
I'll take the food to Shen Yu.

442
00:18:25,480 --> 00:18:26,520
You wait outside.

443
00:18:26,720 --> 00:18:28,000
If he sees you,

444
00:18:28,000 --> 00:18:29,330
the act will fall apart.

445
00:18:42,560 --> 00:18:43,720
You follow this young officer

446
00:18:43,720 --> 00:18:44,760
and bring the lotus leaf porridge

447
00:18:44,760 --> 00:18:46,040
to the Prince's tent.

448
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:47,720
Yes.

449
00:18:48,520 --> 00:18:49,050
Let's go.

450
00:18:56,290 --> 00:18:58,320
Just leave the porridge to me.

451
00:19:00,810 --> 00:19:02,400
Sir, you may not know

452
00:19:02,720 --> 00:19:03,920
that this lotus leaf porridge

453
00:19:03,920 --> 00:19:05,280
has been kept chilled

454
00:19:05,280 --> 00:19:06,320
in a specially

455
00:19:06,320 --> 00:19:08,000
crafted ice container.

456
00:19:08,000 --> 00:19:09,040
It's very delicate.

457
00:19:09,040 --> 00:19:11,000
If you don't know the trick to it and spill it,

458
00:19:11,000 --> 00:19:12,260
that wouldn't be good.

459
00:19:14,520 --> 00:19:15,400
Then please leave quickly

460
00:19:15,400 --> 00:19:16,720
once it's delivered.

461
00:19:16,720 --> 00:19:19,180
Do not disturb the Prince during his duties.

462
00:19:19,440 --> 00:19:21,640
Thank you for your understanding, sir.

463
00:19:36,400 --> 00:19:37,680
What does build

464
00:19:38,040 --> 00:19:40,000
have to do with being tall?

465
00:19:47,280 --> 00:19:49,010
No need to reset the sand table.

466
00:19:49,720 --> 00:19:51,000
I'll take a look first,

467
00:19:51,260 --> 00:19:52,720
then we'll go over the strategy together.

468
00:19:52,720 --> 00:19:53,240
Yes.

469
00:19:53,750 --> 00:19:55,240
I shall take my leave.

470
00:19:57,560 --> 00:19:59,090
It turns out to be a mistake.

471
00:19:59,350 --> 00:20:00,280
Fortunately,

472
00:20:00,610 --> 00:20:02,160
it's not him.

473
00:20:21,930 --> 00:20:23,680
He's refined and upright,

474
00:20:24,020 --> 00:20:25,560
tall and slender,

475
00:20:26,270 --> 00:20:29,200
even seems a bit taller than Second Young Master Shu.

476
00:20:29,350 --> 00:20:30,240
He's definitely not a

477
00:20:30,240 --> 00:20:31,720
rough and burly brute.

478
00:20:42,520 --> 00:20:43,380
Your Highness,

479
00:20:43,430 --> 00:20:45,560
Young General Shen asked me

480
00:20:45,560 --> 00:20:47,880
to bring you lotus leaf porridge.

481
00:20:48,280 --> 00:20:50,240
He said it helps cool the heat.

482
00:20:51,070 --> 00:20:52,040
Put it there.

483
00:21:16,980 --> 00:21:18,480
It's best enjoyed

484
00:21:18,950 --> 00:21:20,970
while still cool.

485
00:21:21,280 --> 00:21:23,000
The flavor is at its peak now.

486
00:21:36,280 --> 00:21:38,240
So he has new boots.

487
00:21:38,880 --> 00:21:39,880
Yet he entered the palace to meet the Emperor

488
00:21:39,880 --> 00:21:42,080
without the slightest regard for proper decorum.

489
00:21:42,080 --> 00:21:43,880
It seems that even if he's not a brute,

490
00:21:43,880 --> 00:21:46,080
he must be an arrogant and reckless man.

491
00:21:48,790 --> 00:21:51,850
His palms are calloused, and his fingertips are rough,

492
00:21:52,240 --> 00:21:54,700
yet the shape of his hands, with broad palms,

493
00:21:54,840 --> 00:21:57,300
slender joints, and clearly defined bones,

494
00:21:57,320 --> 00:21:58,520
is truly beautiful.

495
00:21:59,580 --> 00:22:01,360
Sharp eyebrows and bright eyes,

496
00:22:01,360 --> 00:22:03,020
a straight nose and thin lips—

497
00:22:03,680 --> 00:22:05,880
his looks and presence are truly on par with

498
00:22:05,880 --> 00:22:07,410
Second Young Master Shu's,

499
00:22:07,470 --> 00:22:08,880
even carrying a

500
00:22:09,480 --> 00:22:11,810
noble, cold elegance like polished jade.

501
00:22:13,260 --> 00:22:13,960
Wait.

502
00:22:14,140 --> 00:22:15,070
Where have I seen

503
00:22:15,450 --> 00:22:17,240
him before?

504
00:22:23,080 --> 00:22:24,440
Why are you here?

505
00:22:25,530 --> 00:22:26,540
Have you seen enough?

506
00:22:26,540 --> 00:22:27,880
Why are you here?

507
00:22:30,270 --> 00:22:32,600
Your Highness, a message from the palace.

508
00:22:35,350 --> 00:22:36,320
Your Highness?

509
00:22:36,320 --> 00:22:37,000
Say it.

510
00:22:37,000 --> 00:22:39,080
Regarding On Military Discipline and Morale you wrote,

511
00:22:39,080 --> 00:22:40,000
the Emperor has ordered

512
00:22:40,000 --> 00:22:41,280
the Hanlin Academy to copy it carefully

513
00:22:41,280 --> 00:22:42,720
and compile it along with

514
00:22:42,720 --> 00:22:43,960
several other military essays

515
00:22:43,960 --> 00:22:45,720
you previously wrote into a volume.

516
00:22:45,720 --> 00:22:47,520
What are your instructions?

517
00:22:48,310 --> 00:22:50,010
Just follow His Majesty's order.

518
00:22:50,010 --> 00:22:52,340
Yes, I shall take my leave.

519
00:22:53,580 --> 00:22:55,240
He can write articles too?

520
00:23:00,240 --> 00:23:02,100
Why Miss Ming hasn't come out yet?

521
00:23:02,170 --> 00:23:03,940
Is the Prince of Dingbei giving her a hard time?

522
00:23:03,940 --> 00:23:04,960
Will she...

523
00:23:05,880 --> 00:23:06,800
Miss Minmin,

524
00:23:07,040 --> 00:23:08,440
