525
00:23:13,280 --> 00:23:13,960
No,

526
00:23:14,520 --> 00:23:16,480
Tan is always careful,

527
00:23:16,480 --> 00:23:17,320
especially with important matters.

528
00:23:17,320 --> 00:23:18,370
She wouldn't mess up.

529
00:23:18,370 --> 00:23:19,000
Besides,

530
00:23:19,000 --> 00:23:20,040
she's the Emperor's appointed

531
00:23:20,040 --> 00:23:21,000
Princess of Dingbei.

532
00:23:21,000 --> 00:23:22,250
No matter how domineering the Prince of Dingbei is,

533
00:23:22,250 --> 00:23:23,520
he won't trouble her.

534
00:23:25,200 --> 00:23:26,960
If she still

535
00:23:27,240 --> 00:23:29,000
hasn't come out

536
00:23:29,040 --> 00:23:30,080
after a cup of tea's time,

537
00:23:30,080 --> 00:23:31,140
then we can rush in.

538
00:23:31,810 --> 00:23:32,280
You...

539
00:23:33,520 --> 00:23:35,180
Are you the Prince of Dingbei?

540
00:23:35,640 --> 00:23:37,990
Could it be that I'm still just a bandit?

541
00:23:38,440 --> 00:23:40,240
That day at the Duke of Ling's Mansion,

542
00:23:40,240 --> 00:23:41,500
you weren't stealing?

543
00:23:41,720 --> 00:23:43,210
Those official silver shipments

544
00:23:43,210 --> 00:23:45,940
were military payrolls hijacked by Liang Qiwei.

545
00:23:48,210 --> 00:23:49,930
And what about Hanyan Temple?

546
00:23:50,150 --> 00:23:51,690
The Sheriff searching the temple

547
00:23:51,690 --> 00:23:53,530
colluded with the Haiyou Sect.

548
00:23:53,920 --> 00:23:55,440
They blocked my entry to the capital

549
00:23:55,440 --> 00:23:56,840
precisely to obstruct my

550
00:23:57,080 --> 00:23:59,210
investigation into the payroll case.

551
00:23:59,240 --> 00:24:00,500
Is there any question?

552
00:24:02,990 --> 00:24:05,000
Let me think about it.

553
00:24:07,160 --> 00:24:07,720
Sit.

554
00:24:16,480 --> 00:24:18,480
Wait, why would you want to marry me?

555
00:24:20,090 --> 00:24:21,760
May Buddha grant me

556
00:24:21,760 --> 00:24:23,560
a suitable husband.

557
00:24:23,580 --> 00:24:25,040
His appearance must be handsome,

558
00:24:25,040 --> 00:24:26,320
I'm good-looking.

559
00:24:26,320 --> 00:24:28,200
only then would he be a match for me.

560
00:24:28,200 --> 00:24:29,680
I'm over seven feet tall.

561
00:24:29,720 --> 00:24:31,200
In stature,

562
00:24:31,220 --> 00:24:32,410
may he stand over seven feet tall.

563
00:24:32,410 --> 00:24:33,540
My parents are dead.

564
00:24:33,540 --> 00:24:34,610
I also pray that my future mother-in-law

565
00:24:34,610 --> 00:24:35,270
does not burden me with endless rules,

566
00:24:35,270 --> 00:24:36,510
I don't have mother who set rules

567
00:24:36,510 --> 00:24:37,080
and nitpicking.

568
00:24:37,080 --> 00:24:38,560
and nitpick every day.

569
00:24:39,140 --> 00:24:41,160
My family relationship is also simple.

