00:24:42,150 --> 00:24:44,230
beyond a few close friends,

572
00:24:44,560 --> 00:24:46,590
I maintain no unnecessary social ties.

573
00:24:46,590 --> 00:24:48,720
-Above all, there must be no childhood sweethearts
-I have no childhood sweethearts.

574
00:24:48,720 --> 00:24:50,680
or overly intimate cousin-sisters lingering about.

575
00:24:50,680 --> 00:24:51,480
In that case,

576
00:24:52,520 --> 00:24:53,980
do you have any questions?

577
00:24:55,440 --> 00:24:56,440
No.

578
00:24:57,400 --> 00:24:58,850
Regarding talent,

579
00:24:58,880 --> 00:25:00,160
I ranked beyond the top imperial examinees.

580
00:25:00,160 --> 00:25:01,860
Bird's nest porridge is always available.

581
00:25:01,860 --> 00:25:04,320
He must at least provide me
with bird's nest porridge whenever I desire,

582
00:25:04,320 --> 00:25:06,050
and afford seasonal wardrobes

583
00:25:06,220 --> 00:25:08,080
from Brocade Splendor Workshop.

584
00:25:08,370 --> 00:25:10,900
So, do you have any questions?

585
00:25:15,740 --> 00:25:17,220
I'm strong and healthy

586
00:25:17,590 --> 00:25:19,010
without crude bulk.

587
00:25:19,290 --> 00:25:20,490
If anything happens,

588
00:25:20,560 --> 00:25:22,290
I can safeguard you unscathed should danger arise.

589
00:25:22,290 --> 00:25:23,960
My weapon of choice is the sword,

590
00:25:23,960 --> 00:25:25,520
wielded with appreciable grace.

591
00:25:25,520 --> 00:25:27,040
-When he wields his blade,
-When you play the qin,

592
00:25:27,040 --> 00:25:29,000
-I may accompany him with the qin, creating a scene of perfect harmony.
-I can wield my blade, creating a scene of perfect harmony.

593
00:25:29,000 --> 00:25:29,960
Wait.

594
00:25:30,320 --> 00:25:33,000
These words sound eerily familiar.

595
00:25:33,620 --> 00:25:34,560
How could you know

596
00:25:34,560 --> 00:25:35,760
my marital criteria?

597
00:25:36,310 --> 00:25:37,480
If every item

598
00:25:37,480 --> 00:25:39,080
matches your requirements,

599
00:25:39,240 --> 00:25:40,570
why shouldn't I wed you?

600
00:25:40,720 --> 00:25:42,080
Someone like the Prince of Dingbei,

601
00:25:42,080 --> 00:25:43,760
who treads blades and drinks blood—

602
00:25:43,760 --> 00:25:44,720
how could an ordinary woman like me

603
00:25:44,720 --> 00:25:46,720
dare aspire to that?

604
00:25:46,920 --> 00:25:48,200
They said you're a tyrannical

605
00:25:48,200 --> 00:25:49,040
butcher...

606
00:25:49,720 --> 00:25:50,800
They also said that

607
00:25:50,800 --> 00:25:52,040
beneath my mansion's peonies

608
00:25:52,040 --> 00:25:52,520
lie the mutilated

609
00:25:52,520 --> 00:25:54,000
corpses of my concubines.

610
00:25:56,340 --> 00:25:58,240
Then... Are those rumors

611
00:25:59,960 --> 00:26:01,000
true or false?

612
00:26:05,000 --> 00:26:07,000
I only kill those who deserve death.

613
00:26:16,300 --> 00:26:18,440
Even if you meet all my criteria,

614
00:26:19,080 --> 00:26:21,720
that doesn't mean I must marry you.

615
00:26:24,760 --> 00:26:25,680
Don't you want to?

616
00:26:25,680 --> 00:26:27,440
It's not about whether I want to or not.

617
00:26:27,440 --> 00:26:28,480
The truth is, we share

618
00:26:28,480 --> 00:26:29,960
no affection,

619
00:26:30,000 --> 00:26:31,080
and our temperaments

620
00:26:31,080 --> 00:26:32,410
clash far too severely.

621
00:26:32,480 --> 00:26:33,800
Should we wed,

622
00:26:34,760 --> 00:26:36,620
our household would descend into

623
00:26:37,000 --> 00:26:38,240
ceaseless turmoil—

624
00:26:38,560 --> 00:26:39,960
no peace for man or beast.

625
00:26:43,200 --> 00:26:44,860
Who do you love in the capital?

626
00:26:45,520 --> 00:26:47,120
Whom would you rather marry?

627
00:26:49,080 --> 00:26:50,240
If I don't wed you,

628
00:26:51,200 --> 00:26:51,860
His Majesty

629
00:26:52,440 --> 00:26:53,160
will simply

630
00:26:53,160 --> 00:26:54,420
decree another match.

631
00:27:00,110 --> 00:27:01,970
Becoming the Princess of Dingbei

632
00:27:02,500 --> 00:27:03,480
is the optimal choice

633
00:27:03,480 --> 00:27:06,270
for both the Marquis of Jing'an and the Ming family.

634
00:27:06,270 --> 00:27:07,800
Must I

635
00:27:09,590 --> 00:27:11,050
state such obvious logic?

636
00:27:17,020 --> 00:27:18,640
You imply

637
00:27:20,000 --> 00:27:21,240
a marriage of

638
00:27:22,000 --> 00:27:23,730
convenience between us, then.

639
00:27:24,050 --> 00:27:26,240
No expectation of conjugal affection,

640
00:27:26,240 --> 00:27:27,080
merely

641
00:27:27,520 --> 00:27:30,160
mutual benefit between our houses.

642
00:27:35,040 --> 00:27:37,440
You may interpret it thus.

643
00:27:43,300 --> 00:27:44,240
-Tan!
-My Lady!

644
00:27:44,260 --> 00:27:45,680
You finally came out.

645
00:27:47,720 --> 00:27:48,440
How are you?

646
00:27:53,480 --> 00:27:54,640
Say something.

647
00:27:54,760 --> 00:27:55,720
Did you see him?

648
00:27:56,760 --> 00:27:58,520
What happened?

649
00:27:58,520 --> 00:28:00,120
Why are you all dumbfounded?

650
00:28:02,000 --> 00:28:04,760
He's undeniably formidable in presence.

651
00:28:07,010 --> 00:28:08,240
How does he look?

652
00:28:09,110 --> 00:28:09,570
Well...

653
00:28:10,850 --> 00:28:12,920
Don't tell me he's worse-looking than Uncle!

654
00:28:12,920 --> 00:28:14,440
What standards does Uncle have?

655
00:28:14,440 --> 00:28:15,440
Even the finest warrior

656
00:28:15,440 --> 00:28:17,440
can't compensate for boorishness!

657
00:28:18,390 --> 00:28:19,800
Who said he was boorish?

658
00:28:20,280 --> 00:28:20,760
Minmin,

659
00:28:20,960 --> 00:28:23,480
have you ever heard of On Military Discipline and Morale?

660
00:28:23,480 --> 00:28:24,040
What treatise?

661
00:28:24,040 --> 00:28:24,920
On Military Discipline and Morale?

662
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:26,280
At last year's literary gathering,

663
00:28:26,280 --> 00:28:27,160
I heard two young scholars

664
00:28:27,160 --> 00:28:28,420
debate this very text.

665
00:28:28,760 --> 00:28:30,720
I don't understand military tactics,

666
00:28:30,720 --> 00:28:31,880
but just from his discussion,

667
00:28:31,880 --> 00:28:33,720
I can tell his writing is logically tight,

668
00:28:33,720 --> 00:28:35,720
concise, and sharp.

669
00:28:36,240 --> 00:28:37,440
Later, when visiting your house,

670
00:28:37,440 --> 00:28:38,680
Uncle praised it as

671
00:28:38,860 --> 00:28:40,400
"groundbreaking in substance,

672
00:28:40,400 --> 00:28:42,060
devoid of hollow sophistry."

673
00:28:44,040 --> 00:28:44,880
Did he?

674
00:28:45,270 --> 00:28:46,680
I don't recall.

675
00:28:47,800 --> 00:28:49,720
What does this have to do with the Prince of Dingbei?

676
00:28:49,720 --> 00:28:51,640
One thing he's right about—

677
00:28:52,640 --> 00:28:54,500
with his abilities, strategies,

678
00:28:54,950 --> 00:28:56,480
and influence,

679
00:28:59,000 --> 00:29:01,490
he would indeed greatly benefit the Ming family.

680
00:29:01,490 --> 00:29:04,160
Then will you call off the engagement or not?

681
00:29:05,520 --> 00:29:07,650
Today has brought too many surprises.

682
00:29:08,040 --> 00:29:09,280
Let me think about it.

683
00:29:16,960 --> 00:29:18,030
Wait a moment.

684
00:29:20,440 --> 00:29:22,900
[Prince of Dingbei's Mansion]

685
00:29:29,560 --> 00:29:30,420
Your Highness,

686
00:29:30,480 --> 00:29:32,240
the offerings for tomorrow's incense ceremony

687
00:29:32,240 --> 00:29:33,440
at Hanyan Temple

688
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,680
await your approval.

689
00:29:46,030 --> 00:29:46,720
Your Highness,

690
00:29:46,720 --> 00:29:48,560
here are last month's accounts

691
00:29:46,970 --> 00:29:48,200
[Cuojin Pavilion Ledgers] [Jinxiu Workshop Ledgers]

692
00:29:48,560 --> 00:29:51,160
from the Cuojin Pavilion and Jinxiu Workshop.

693
00:29:53,880 --> 00:29:55,640
I'll take my leave then.

694
00:30:03,000 --> 00:30:05,800
Your Highness, have some midnight refreshments.

695
00:30:07,000 --> 00:30:07,680
Uncle Fu,

696
00:30:08,720 --> 00:30:10,320
speak your mind.

697
00:30:11,240 --> 00:30:13,040
I'll say it then.

698
00:30:13,480 --> 00:30:14,720
I heard that His Majesty

699
00:30:14,720 --> 00:30:15,920
has arranged your marriage with

700
00:30:15,920 --> 00:30:17,800
the Fourth Miss of Ming family.

701
00:30:19,310 --> 00:30:20,560
I think

702
00:30:20,560 --> 00:30:22,040
the imperial match

703
00:30:22,040 --> 00:30:23,040
is great.

704
00:30:23,720 --> 00:30:24,360
Tell me.

705
00:30:24,920 --> 00:30:25,870
What exactly is so good?

706
00:30:25,870 --> 00:30:26,520
Your Highness,

707
00:30:26,520 --> 00:30:27,440
you've been occupied with

708
00:30:27,440 --> 00:30:29,240
battles and military affairs these past years,

709
00:30:29,240 --> 00:30:30,200
so naturally you wouldn't pay much attention to

710
00:30:30,200 --> 00:30:31,920
the noble young ladies in the capital.

711
00:30:31,920 --> 00:30:33,240
But I know well.

712
00:30:33,260 --> 00:30:34,720
This Fourth Miss of the Ming family

713
00:30:34,720 --> 00:30:35,960
truly stands out

714
00:30:36,000 --> 00:30:38,320
among all the noble girls in the capital.

715
00:30:38,340 --> 00:30:39,520
Her looks and family background

716
00:30:39,520 --> 00:30:40,560
speak for themselves,

717
00:30:40,560 --> 00:30:42,040
and in terms of talent,

718
00:30:42,040 --> 00:30:43,480
she is second to none—

719
00:30:43,480 --> 00:30:45,040
skilled in music, chess, calligraphy, and painting.

720
00:30:45,040 --> 00:30:46,640
It is especially her skill with the qin

721
00:30:46,640 --> 00:30:48,800
that is unmatched in the capital,

722
00:30:48,800 --> 00:30:50,530
leaving all others far behind.

723
00:30:53,680 --> 00:30:54,720
The most important thing is that

724
00:30:54,720 --> 00:30:57,000
the Fourth Miss from the Ming family is gentle, kind, and graceful

725
00:30:57,000 --> 00:30:58,240
with a heart as pure as orchids.

726
00:30:58,240 --> 00:31:00,440
She treats others with genuine warmth.

727
00:31:01,950 --> 00:31:03,220
Your Highness, you...

728
00:31:04,710 --> 00:31:05,460
She is

729
00:31:06,370 --> 00:31:07,270
kind?

730
00:31:07,300 --> 00:31:08,920
Of course.

731
00:31:10,720 --> 00:31:13,040
Two years ago, when the Cuojin Pavilion had just opened,

732
00:31:13,040 --> 00:31:14,680
war broke out in the North.

733
00:31:14,720 --> 00:31:16,560
That scoundrel in the Ministry of Revenue embezzled military funds

734
00:31:16,560 --> 00:31:17,680
and deceived his superiors.

735
00:31:17,680 --> 00:31:19,000
Your Highness sent word for

736
00:31:19,000 --> 00:31:21,730
the princely manor to raise the funds in advance.

737
00:31:21,800 --> 00:31:24,640
But across three separate occasions,

738
00:31:24,720 --> 00:31:26,920
the total sum amounted to hundreds of thousands of taels of silver!

739
00:31:26,920 --> 00:31:29,640
These estate businesses were already running deficits.

740
00:31:29,640 --> 00:31:31,080
Where could we suddenly procure

741
00:31:31,080 --> 00:31:32,520
so much silver?

742
00:31:32,800 --> 00:31:34,560
Even selling shops or land

743
00:31:34,680 --> 00:31:37,200
would require time to liquidate.

744
00:31:37,610 --> 00:31:38,760
Fortunately,

745
00:31:38,780 --> 00:31:40,760
Miss Ming began frequenting our establishments during that period,

746
00:31:40,760 --> 00:31:42,880
spending considerable sums.

747
00:31:44,750 --> 00:31:46,170
Though she never stated her purpose,

748
00:31:46,170 --> 00:31:48,050
I recognized her true intent:

749
00:31:48,390 --> 00:31:49,760
finding pretexts

750
00:31:49,760 --> 00:31:51,440
to donate military funds.

751
00:31:53,110 --> 00:31:54,340
After Miss Ming set the trend,

752
00:31:54,340 --> 00:31:55,980
noblewomen from the capital

753
00:31:56,040 --> 00:31:57,240
followed suit in emulation—

754
00:31:57,240 --> 00:31:58,000
only then was

755
00:31:58,000 --> 00:32:00,400
your urgent financial crisis alleviated.

756
00:32:02,360 --> 00:32:03,290
By that measure,

757
00:32:04,100 --> 00:32:06,330
her contribution to the Dongzhou victory was significant?

758
00:32:06,330 --> 00:32:08,230
That's a great merit.

759
00:32:08,260 --> 00:32:10,640
Anyway, this marriage decree is most fortuitous.

760
00:32:10,640 --> 00:32:11,680
One might say the prince and princess

761
00:32:11,680 --> 00:32:13,560
are a match made by heaven itself.

762
00:32:14,300 --> 00:32:15,580
I've thought about it.

763
00:32:15,610 --> 00:32:17,610
I planned to present the princess

764
00:32:17,630 --> 00:32:19,260
with a full headdress set from the Cuojin Pavilion.

765
00:32:19,260 --> 00:32:20,390
Our future Princess

766
00:32:20,410 --> 00:32:21,800
must be the most splendid bride

767
00:32:21,800 --> 00:32:23,640
in the capital.

768
00:32:32,180 --> 00:32:32,900
Father.

769
00:32:38,300 --> 00:32:40,300
Father, working late into the night

770
00:32:40,510 --> 00:32:41,640
must be exhausting.

771
00:32:42,110 --> 00:32:43,160
I've prepared

772
00:32:43,160 --> 00:32:44,420
mung bean and lily soup

773
00:32:44,720 --> 00:32:46,920
to relieve the summer heat and fatigue.

774
00:32:48,000 --> 00:32:48,400
Sit.

775
00:32:59,640 --> 00:33:01,640
Why are you still awake at this hour?

776
00:33:06,060 --> 00:33:07,700
Thoughts of marriage

777
00:33:08,680 --> 00:33:10,000
keep me restless.

778
00:33:16,200 --> 00:33:17,520
I've never imagined

779
00:33:18,080 --> 00:33:21,140
what life would be like outside the Marquis's mansion,

780
00:33:21,680 --> 00:33:22,640
nor do I know

781
00:33:23,600 --> 00:33:24,800
what awaits me

782
00:33:25,650 --> 00:33:27,240
in another household.

783
00:33:37,860 --> 00:33:38,700
Tan,

784
00:33:40,640 --> 00:33:42,500
though I may be careless at times,

785
00:33:43,560 --> 00:33:44,520
I do know

786
00:33:44,520 --> 00:33:46,320
you're feeling uneasy

787
00:33:46,320 --> 00:33:48,050
about this arranged marriage.

788
00:33:51,480 --> 00:33:52,480
Don't worry.

789
00:33:53,610 --> 00:33:56,000
The Prince of Dingbei is a good man.

790
00:33:59,410 --> 00:34:02,270
Is Father's judgment towards the Prince of Dingbei

791
00:34:02,460 --> 00:34:04,220
just a "good man"?

792
00:34:09,679 --> 00:34:11,679
You have no idea that

793
00:34:13,699 --> 00:34:15,040
during an autumn hunt

794
00:34:15,040 --> 00:34:16,560
in the late emperor's reign,

795
00:34:16,560 --> 00:34:18,600
His Majesty—who was then still the Crown Prince—

796
00:34:18,600 --> 00:34:19,800
was ambushed in the forest

797
00:34:19,800 --> 00:34:21,320
by assassins.

798
00:34:21,400 --> 00:34:22,480
It was the Prince of Dingbei

799
00:34:22,480 --> 00:34:25,590
who charged in alone, fought through the encirclement,

800
00:34:25,590 --> 00:34:28,989
and protected His Majesty despite being seriously wounded.

801
00:34:31,639 --> 00:34:34,360
No wonder His Majesty trusts him so deeply.

802
00:34:34,480 --> 00:34:35,320
Yes.

803
00:34:36,840 --> 00:34:38,560
It's said that the issue of the Dingbei Army's military funds

804
00:34:38,560 --> 00:34:40,520
has been festering for years.

805
00:34:41,520 --> 00:34:42,440
Two years ago,

806
00:34:42,440 --> 00:34:44,480
the former Vice Minister of Revenue's

807
00:34:44,480 --> 00:34:47,159
embezzlement disrupted the northern war effort.

808
00:34:47,159 --> 00:34:48,639
After narrowly

809
00:34:48,639 --> 00:34:50,199
surviving the battlefield,

810
00:34:50,199 --> 00:34:52,120
the first thing the Prince of Dingbei did upon returning

811
00:34:52,120 --> 00:34:53,760
was storm into the vice minister's residence

812
00:34:53,760 --> 00:34:55,480
and take his head—

813
00:34:56,440 --> 00:34:58,160
seeking justice

814
00:34:58,160 --> 00:35:00,220
for the soldiers of the Dingbei Army.

815
00:35:04,080 --> 00:35:06,120
He's certainly a man of fierce resolve.

816
00:35:06,120 --> 00:35:07,760
Just last year, the battle in Dongzhou

817
00:35:07,760 --> 00:35:09,280
left the land soaked in blood

818
00:35:09,280 --> 00:35:10,810
and littered with corpses.

819
00:35:11,160 --> 00:35:13,090
That's probably why he returned to

820
00:35:13,760 --> 00:35:16,490
the capital to investigate the case personally.

821
00:35:22,880 --> 00:35:25,040
But Father, I was originally

822
00:35:25,040 --> 00:35:27,300
supposed to marry into the Liang family.

823
00:35:27,520 --> 00:35:28,440
Now that you've

824
00:35:28,680 --> 00:35:30,480
accepted His Majesty's decree,

825
00:35:31,120 --> 00:35:33,320
doesn't that mean you've taken a stand?

826
00:35:34,120 --> 00:35:35,320
Won't it be difficult

827
00:35:37,120 --> 00:35:38,650
to explain things to my godfather?

828
00:35:38,650 --> 00:35:39,170
Wait,

829
00:35:39,200 --> 00:35:40,300
he picked a bad husband for you,

830
00:35:40,300 --> 00:35:41,770
yet he never thought he owed anyone an explanation.

831
00:35:41,770 --> 00:35:42,430
Why should I need to

832
00:35:42,430 --> 00:35:43,870
explain anything to him?

833
00:35:51,000 --> 00:35:53,250
Then do you truly think that the Prince of Dingbei

834
00:35:53,250 --> 00:35:55,290
is someone worthy of entrusting

835
00:35:56,170 --> 00:35:59,030
both your daughter and the Ming family's future to?

836
00:36:00,280 --> 00:36:01,080
Tan,

837
00:36:02,040 --> 00:36:03,040
remember this—

838
00:36:03,920 --> 00:36:06,380
the Ming family will always have my backing.

839
00:36:06,440 --> 00:36:08,120
You don't have to sacrifice your whole life

840
00:36:08,120 --> 00:36:09,600
just to please our family.

841
00:36:10,400 --> 00:36:12,480
Whether it's you or Chu,

842
00:36:12,640 --> 00:36:15,280
you only need to choose the man you truly like.

843
00:36:15,580 --> 00:36:17,640
No need to worry about anything else.

844
00:36:18,820 --> 00:36:19,740
Father.

845
00:36:20,480 --> 00:36:22,640
As for your marriage,

846
00:36:23,120 --> 00:36:24,650
even though it's arranged,

847
00:36:26,560 --> 00:36:29,480
I have thought it through carefully.

848
00:36:30,080 --> 00:36:31,880
Look around all of Xian;

849
00:36:32,760 --> 00:36:34,360
aside from the Emperor himself,

850
00:36:34,360 --> 00:36:36,440
if even the Prince of Dingbei can't protect you,

851
00:36:36,440 --> 00:36:37,800
then no one else

852
00:36:37,800 --> 00:36:39,280
has the ability to do so.

853
00:36:39,800 --> 00:36:42,080
So I can rest assured that

854
00:36:43,160 --> 00:36:44,960
this marriage will benefit you.

