00:36:55,060 --> 00:36:58,070
[Prince of Dingbei's Mansion]

856
00:37:09,600 --> 00:37:10,840
I really don't understand

857
00:37:10,840 --> 00:37:12,560
why His Majesty would arrange this marriage.

858
00:37:12,560 --> 00:37:14,040
Marquis of Jing'an commands Yangxi Prefecture,

859
00:37:14,040 --> 00:37:15,700
and you lead the Dingbei Army.

860
00:37:15,760 --> 00:37:17,080
With such overwhelming military power,

861
00:37:17,080 --> 00:37:17,760
wouldn't the Emperor

862
00:37:17,760 --> 00:37:19,280
have some reservations?

863
00:37:19,840 --> 00:37:20,760
Since when did you start worrying about

864
00:37:20,760 --> 00:37:22,160
the Emperor's thoughts?

865
00:37:24,560 --> 00:37:25,420
What about you?

866
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:27,280
Are you willing to

867
00:37:27,480 --> 00:37:28,740
accept this marriage?

868
00:37:29,440 --> 00:37:30,840
Didn't you say

869
00:37:31,000 --> 00:37:33,530
it wouldn't be impossible for me to marry her?

870
00:37:34,380 --> 00:37:34,960
Well...

871
00:37:36,120 --> 00:37:37,600
That was just a joke.

872
00:37:38,510 --> 00:37:39,600
I only meant that

873
00:37:39,890 --> 00:37:41,360
if you're not sincere about marrying her,

874
00:37:41,360 --> 00:37:42,200
you shouldn't waste

875
00:37:42,200 --> 00:37:43,320
the girl's life.

