00:37:45,820 --> 00:37:46,320
then...

879
00:37:49,330 --> 00:37:50,810
Wouldn't that be my fault?

880
00:37:50,840 --> 00:37:52,430
If you don't want to marry her,

881
00:37:52,430 --> 00:37:53,470
nor me,

882
00:37:54,450 --> 00:37:55,730
then what do you think

883
00:37:55,850 --> 00:37:56,910
will become of her?

884
00:37:58,640 --> 00:37:59,360
Well...

885
00:37:59,630 --> 00:38:01,290
Nowadays, which noble family

886
00:38:01,300 --> 00:38:02,300
in the capital

887
00:38:02,330 --> 00:38:04,520
can truly match the prestige of the Ming family

888
00:38:04,520 --> 00:38:06,450
without affecting court affairs?

889
00:38:07,520 --> 00:38:10,450
These noble daughters are born into great families,

890
00:38:10,520 --> 00:38:12,440
so their fate is never entirely their own.

891
00:38:12,440 --> 00:38:13,680
Their honor and disgrace

892
00:38:13,680 --> 00:38:16,410
are inevitably tied to their family's standing.

893
00:38:18,640 --> 00:38:19,920
Whether my intentions are sincere

894
00:38:19,920 --> 00:38:21,120
or merely practical,

895
00:38:21,480 --> 00:38:22,880
since she is my princess,

896
00:38:23,840 --> 00:38:25,500
I will accept her temperament

897
00:38:27,130 --> 00:38:28,530
and protect her for life.

898
00:38:33,220 --> 00:38:34,060
Mother,

899
00:38:35,600 --> 00:38:38,000
I have some doubts.

900
00:38:38,770 --> 00:38:40,440
I was reluctant about this marriage

901
00:38:40,440 --> 00:38:41,840
arranged by the Emperor.

902
00:38:43,080 --> 00:38:45,880
I had thought those who fight on the battlefield

903
00:38:46,160 --> 00:38:47,680
would be like Father—

904
00:38:48,640 --> 00:38:49,920
brave and rough.

905
00:38:51,750 --> 00:38:53,710
But after meeting him once,

906
00:38:55,160 --> 00:38:56,320
I didn't expect him

907
00:38:57,090 --> 00:38:58,500
to be handsome

908
00:38:58,800 --> 00:38:59,920
and dignified,

909
00:39:00,820 --> 00:39:02,660
nothing like the rumors said.

910
00:39:06,200 --> 00:39:07,440
It seems that

911
00:39:08,880 --> 00:39:12,840
the Prince of Dingbei, in terms of family background,

912
00:39:13,280 --> 00:39:14,800
appearance, and talent,

913
00:39:15,600 --> 00:39:16,880
meets all the criteria

914
00:39:17,220 --> 00:39:19,020
I had

915
00:39:19,130 --> 00:39:20,290
for a husband.

916
00:39:20,750 --> 00:39:24,900
[Memorial Tablet of Bai Feiyuan of the Ming Family]

917
00:39:21,480 --> 00:39:22,840
I originally thought,

918
00:39:23,320 --> 00:39:24,840
because of his bad reputation,

919
00:39:24,840 --> 00:39:26,440
that he must be a cold-blooded and cruel man

920
00:39:26,440 --> 00:39:27,880
of poor character.

921
00:39:29,320 --> 00:39:30,320
But just now,

922
00:39:30,760 --> 00:39:32,480
Father's sincere words

923
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:35,800
have dispelled those doubts from my heart.

924
00:39:36,200 --> 00:39:37,600
Father has certainly

925
00:39:37,600 --> 00:39:39,860
given this careful thought on my behalf.

926
00:39:40,480 --> 00:39:41,920
According to Father,

927
00:39:42,680 --> 00:39:45,480
he is indeed a man

928
00:39:46,000 --> 00:39:47,680
worthy of trust.

929
00:39:50,600 --> 00:39:51,480
However,

930
00:39:54,000 --> 00:39:56,440
I know very little about him

931
00:39:56,880 --> 00:39:59,730
and don't know if, once we truly get to know each other,

932
00:39:59,730 --> 00:40:02,880
he will be as loyal and honorable

933
00:40:03,000 --> 00:40:04,800
as Father said.

934
00:40:08,820 --> 00:40:11,040
So I still have

935
00:40:11,040 --> 00:40:12,600
some doubts in my heart,

936
00:40:13,560 --> 00:40:15,620
unsure whether I should marry or not.

937
00:40:18,040 --> 00:40:19,080
If Mother hears

938
00:40:19,080 --> 00:40:20,320
my honest thoughts,

939
00:40:21,560 --> 00:40:23,000
could you please tell me

940
00:40:25,480 --> 00:40:26,200
whether you

941
00:40:27,120 --> 00:40:29,000
approve of this marriage?

942
00:40:40,960 --> 00:40:42,560
Mother didn't say anything,

943
00:40:42,600 --> 00:40:44,280
so I took it as your

944
00:40:44,280 --> 00:40:46,080
silent approval

945
00:40:46,560 --> 00:40:48,120
of this marriage.

946
00:40:50,000 --> 00:40:52,040
After I receive the imperial marriage decree,

947
00:40:52,040 --> 00:40:53,590
Chu's wedding

948
00:40:53,680 --> 00:40:55,000
will also be arranged.

949
00:40:56,040 --> 00:40:58,280
Once Chu and I have married,

950
00:40:59,320 --> 00:41:00,680
there will be no one left

951
00:41:02,520 --> 00:41:04,000
in this large Marquis's mansion

952
00:41:04,000 --> 00:41:05,260
to keep Father company

953
00:41:05,840 --> 00:41:07,240
and care for him closely.

954
00:41:08,840 --> 00:41:10,570
Father's return to the capital

955
00:41:11,320 --> 00:41:13,920
naturally fills my heart with joy.

956
00:41:16,120 --> 00:41:17,480
I also wish to

957
00:41:18,120 --> 00:41:20,040
grow closer to him.

958
00:41:22,080 --> 00:41:22,520
But

959
00:41:25,360 --> 00:41:28,000
perhaps because we haven't seen each other for many years,

960
00:41:28,000 --> 00:41:29,120
I still feel

961
00:41:30,000 --> 00:41:31,200
a bit of

962
00:41:34,000 --> 00:41:35,680
awkwardness between us.

963
00:41:37,200 --> 00:41:38,600
But don't worry, Mother.

964
00:41:39,050 --> 00:41:40,290
I will

965
00:41:40,400 --> 00:41:42,120
come back often

966
00:41:43,360 --> 00:41:44,440
to keep both Father

967
00:41:45,040 --> 00:41:46,080
and you company.

968
00:42:17,380 --> 00:42:21,080
[Marquis of Jing'an's Mansion]

969
00:42:22,740 --> 00:42:24,950
[The Sun and Moon Rise Eternally]

970
00:42:37,840 --> 00:42:44,790
[Faint Mist and Drifting Clouds]

971
00:42:39,600 --> 00:42:40,230
Stop!

972
00:42:41,400 --> 00:42:43,000
Are your eyes on the top of your head?

973
00:42:43,000 --> 00:42:44,800
Didn't you see me standing here?

974
00:42:44,880 --> 00:42:46,200
Greetings, Miss Chu.

975
00:42:48,840 --> 00:42:50,480
Yesterday I asked for goat milk,

976
00:42:50,480 --> 00:42:51,760
and the kitchen told me there was none.

977
00:42:51,760 --> 00:42:52,840
How is it that there's suddenly enough

978
00:42:52,840 --> 00:42:54,250
to send to Zhaoshui House this morning?

979
00:42:54,250 --> 00:42:55,210
Miss Chu,

980
00:42:55,360 --> 00:42:56,200
the kitchen

981
00:42:56,200 --> 00:42:58,280
indeed hasn't purchased fresh goat milk lately.

982
00:42:58,280 --> 00:42:59,960
The goat milk used daily by the Fourth Miss to soak her hands

983
00:42:59,960 --> 00:43:00,840
was specially bought

984
00:43:00,840 --> 00:43:02,170
with her own money.

985
00:43:03,600 --> 00:43:04,760
All these years, Father and I

986
00:43:04,760 --> 00:43:06,160
have suffered out in Yangxi Prefecture,

987
00:43:06,160 --> 00:43:07,560
while she lives in the mansion

988
00:43:07,560 --> 00:43:09,880
indulging in luxury without restraint.

989
00:43:10,640 --> 00:43:12,200
No matter how much she spent,

990
00:43:12,200 --> 00:43:14,200
she has never used the household's public funds.

991
00:43:14,200 --> 00:43:15,880
Just the dowry Madam left behind

992
00:43:15,880 --> 00:43:18,080
is enough to support her for a lifetime.

993
00:43:18,360 --> 00:43:20,280
Besides, the Fourth Miss

994
00:43:20,280 --> 00:43:21,760
is soon to be the Princess of Dingbei.

995
00:43:21,760 --> 00:43:22,680
As someone bound for the royal household,

996
00:43:22,680 --> 00:43:23,800
it is only fitting that her lifestyle

997
00:43:23,800 --> 00:43:24,960
be more refined.

998
00:43:24,960 --> 00:43:26,040
There's nothing excessive about it.

999
00:43:26,040 --> 00:43:27,520
Begging your pardon, I shall take my leave first.

1000
00:43:27,520 --> 00:43:28,760
If the goat's milk sits too long,

1001
00:43:28,760 --> 00:43:29,890
it won't stay fresh.

1002
00:43:31,310 --> 00:43:34,270
[Faint Mist and Drifting Clouds]

1003
00:43:37,760 --> 00:43:39,040
My Lady, please clean your hands.

1004
00:43:39,040 --> 00:43:40,440
It's time for breakfast.

1005
00:43:42,460 --> 00:43:44,120
[Faint Mist and Drifting Clouds]

